161
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:51,000
Project delivers value for business and stakeholders throughout the project.

162
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:56,000
Approach follows a delivery cadence for the project deliverables.

163
00:15:56,000 --> 00:16:01,000
